h":117,"seo":332,"stem":118,"__hash__":333},"docs/docs/6.deploy/10.static.md","静态托管",{"type":232,"value":233,"toc":321},"minimark",[234,239,243,246,250,253,279,290,297,304,308,317],[235,236,238],"h2",{"id":237},"什么是静态托管","什么是静态托管？",[240,241,242],"p",{},"静态托管是一种托管类型，您的网站被构建并作为静态文件（HTML、CSS、JS）进行服务，任何静态文件服务器都可以提供这些文件。",[240,244,245],{},"Nuxt Content 可以使用 Nuxt 预渲染部署到静态托管。",[235,247,249],{"id":248},"使用-ssg-构建","使用 SSG 构建",[240,251,252],{},"要使用静态站点生成构建您的应用，请运行以下命令：",[254,255,260],"pre",{"className":256,"code":257,"language":258,"meta":259,"style":259},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter material-theme material-theme-palenight","npx nuxi generate\n","bash","",[261,262,263],"code",{"__ignoreMap":259},[264,265,268,272,276],"span",{"class":266,"line":267},"line",1,[264,269,271],{"class":270},"sBMFI","npx",[264,273,275],{"class":274},"sfazB"," nuxi",[264,277,278],{"class":274}," generate\n",[280,281,283],"tip",{"icon":282},"i-lucide-check",[240,284,285,286,289],{},"此命令将创建一个包含您的静态站点的 ",[261,287,288],{},"dist/"," 目录。您可以将其上传到任何静态托管服务。",[240,291,292,293,296],{},"Nuxt 将使用内部爬虫自动预渲染所有页面，您可以通过 ",[261,294,295],{},"nitro.prerender"," 选项自定义其行为。",[298,299,301],"note",{"to":300},"https://nuxt.com/docs/getting-started/prerendering",[240,302,303],{},"了解更多关于 Nuxt 预渲染的信息。",[235,305,307],{"id":306},"数据库怎么办","数据库怎么办？",[240,309,310,311,316],{},"Nuxt Content 将使用 ",[312,313,315],"a",{"href":314},"/docs/advanced/database#wasm-sqlite-in-browser","WASM SQLite"," 在浏览器中加载数据库，这样，内容查询发生在客户端导航或操作时时，会在浏览器中运行。",[318,319,320],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sBMFI, html code.shiki .sBMFI{--shiki-light:#E2931D;--shiki-default:#FFCB6B;--shiki-dark:#FFCB6B}html pre.shiki code .sfazB, html code.shiki .sfazB{--shiki-light:#91B859;--shiki-default:#C3E88D;--shiki-dark:#C3E88D}html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration)